data.description: Walk up the driveway and through the welcoming front door into this immaculately maintained home in a peaceful and quiet neighborhood. Richly-appointed spaces include large gathering areas to include 2 living areas, dining area, breakfast area and large master suite with a balcony. This home features a grand entrance with vaulted ceilings, 4 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms. This perfectly designed floor plan and location allows for some privacy upstairs or for hosting large gatherings in the family room, enjoy home cooked meals in the kitchen overlooking the spacious and low-maintenance backyard. The paid off solar system achieves major cost savings, especially during the summertime. Conveniently located to shopping, dining, entertainment, and easily accessible to I-10.
